ic field lines that\ndrape around the bubbles during their supersonic expansion, with suppressed\nperpendicular diffusion across the bubble surface. Possible causes of the\nslight bends of the Fermi bubbles to the west are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Jul 2012 20:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Oct 2012 20:19:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
